title: Episode 244 w/ I Am Athlete Podcast
itunes:title: Episode 244 w/ I Am Athlete Podcast
description:
N.O.R.E. & DJ EFN are the Drink Champs. In this episode, we chop it up with the I Am Athlete Podcast! 

Former NFL Athletes Brandon Marshall, Fred Taylor, Channing Crowder and Chef Nancie join the conversation. We talk about sports, politics, Black Lives Matter, Lebron James and more! 

In this wild episode of DC, the Drunk Uncles hold down their Drink Champs title. 🏆🏆 And our guests... you’ll just have to tune in for that one! 😂

Make some noise!!!

Listen and subscribe at http://www.drinkchamps.com
